sentences.sentence: So we got in our car without caddy, much of our belongings as we can put in there.
sentences.translation: 所以我们就这样上了车，东西车上能带多少就到多少。

sentences.sentence: The logistical component of moving Nanny Caddy and delivering nationwide is not so easy.
sentences.translation: Nanny Caddy的物流和全国递送并不简单。
